snippet.title: Elon Musk’s Ex Wife Exposes His Darkest Secret | Life Stories by Goalcast
snippet.description:
Elon Musk, founder of SpaceX and CEO of Tesla, always found it hard fitting in with others. Hiding his painful secrets - Elon threw himself into his work, amassing huge success as an entrepreneur. But when he got caught up in the middle of a messy divorce with Amber Heard, Elon’s worst fears were realized and he hit a severe breaking point.

﻿﻿﻿﻿What's the deal with Elon’s long history of rocky relationships? And how did GRIMES get in the picture? ﻿Finally the truth about Elon Musk comes out...

Short Inspirational Biographies of Histories Greatest, The Legends, The Famous, The Unsung Heroes. Life changing and Inspiring Life Stories that will give you a new perspective on some of the world's most legendary people
